# HotChocolate Cost Analysis

- **Configure cost analysis to prevent expensive queries**
  - Protects your API from abuse and DoS attacks
  - Example:
    ```csharp
    builder.Services
        .AddGraphQLServer()
        .ModifyCostOptions(options =>
        {
            options.MaxFieldCost = 1000;
            options.MaxTypeCost = 1000;
            options.EnforceCostLimits = true;
            options.ApplyCostDefaults = true;
            options.DefaultResolverCost = 10.0;
        });
    ```
  - Source: Context7/Hot Chocolate docs
